<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "technicalContent/dtd/task.dtd">
<task id="volume-control"
 xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/"> 
  <title>Provide volume control</title> 
  <shortdesc>You can set up a user interface control for sound volume. 
  </shortdesc> 
  <taskbody> 
	 <steps id="steps_ECBCA405518940A28F5E6FDA0B571F36"> 
		<step id="step_A30A2303EE894308B0879451B2BDB17E">
				<cmd> Wait for the MediaPlayer instance to be in a valid status for this command. </cmd>
				<info>Any state except for except RELEASED is valid. </info>
			</step> 
		<step id="step_8D5AD350DB7F49A58FD8E2D3E07CEBC3">
				<cmd>Call the volume set method on the <codeph>MediaPlayer</codeph> instance to set
					the audio volume. </cmd>
				<info>
					<p>
						<codeblock outputclass="syntax actionscript">public function set volume(value:Number):void</codeblock>
					</p>
					<p>The value for the volume represents the requested volume expressed as a
						proportion of the maximum volume, where 0 is silent and 1 is the maximum
						volume. </p>
					<p>
						<table id="table_144A2B1260374FBE8D976194F602DDC7">
							<tgroup cols="2">
								<colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="1.00*"/>
								<colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="2.67*"/>
								<thead>
									<row>
										<entry colname="col1">If the specified volume is </entry>
										<entry colname="col2">The resulting volume is </entry>
									</row>
								</thead>
								<tbody>
									<row>
										<entry colname="col1">Less than 0 </entry>
										<entry colname="col2">0 </entry>
									</row>
									<row>
										<entry colname="col1">Between 0 and 1 </entry>
										<entry colname="col2">The specified volume </entry>
									</row>
									<row>
										<entry colname="col1">Greater than 1 </entry>
										<entry colname="col2">The value divided by 100 and set to
											one of the following values: <ul
												id="ul_8C2282F0EDC44A408820F5768709214F">
												<li id="li_B00BC6F4812D4000891358F762C8E492">The
												result if it is between 0 and 1 </li>
												<li id="li_03B7F30662554F299320040CAC2DEB7A">1 if
												the result is greater than 1 </li>
											</ul>
											<note type="tip">This logic handles values that are
												supplied from clients based on earlier versions of
												the <ph conkeyref="phrases/primetime-sdk-name"/>,
												where volume values ranged from 0 to 100. </note>
										</entry>
									</row>
								</tbody>
							</tgroup>
						</table>
					</p>
				</info>
			</step> 
	 </steps> 
  </taskbody> 
</task> 
